*Muškaraca* je bilo puno na sajmu. (There were a lot of men at the fair.)

Poznajem *muškaraca* koji se bave ribolovom. (I know a man who is into fishing.)

Moj otac se zabavlja sa dvojicom *muškaraca*. (My father is having fun with two men.)

Moj prijatelj je postao prijatelj sa još nekoliko *muškaraca*. (My friend has become friends with some other men.)

Naši susjedi su nedavno imali goste, jednog *muškaraca* i jednu ženu. (Our neighbours recently had guests, one man and one woman.)